From: art-suite conda packaging
Subject: [PATCH] Drop -Werror so art_root_io builds under conda's newer toolchain

Like art/canvas/canvas_root_io, art_root_io uses cet_set_compiler_flags(...
VIGILANT WERROR ...). Under conda-forge's newer libstdc++/GCC and ROOT-dictionary
generated code, vigilant warnings become hard errors. Drop -Werror to match the
binary FNAL ships. See conda/potential_improvements.md (#2).

--- a/CMakeLists.txt	2026-06-19 12:47:22.831070572 -0700
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt	2026-06-19 12:47:22.831070572 -0700
@@ -7,7 +7,6 @@
 cet_cmake_env()
 
 cet_set_compiler_flags(DIAGS VIGILANT DWARF_VER 4
-  WERROR
   NO_UNDEFINED
   EXTRA_FLAGS -pedantic)
 
